Package GenotypeGraph

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GenotypeGraph
    Basic class to represent directed graphs about genotypes.
    GenotypeGraphSimple
    Generates a graph connecting all nodes with equal genotypes but for a single extra mutation in the receiver of the edge
    GenotypeMarkovNode
    TODO re-implement with adjacency matrix if needed
    GenotypeNode
    A base class for a single node from a genotype graph (based on adjacency matrix)
    Main  
    WeightedGenotypeGraph
    A very simple method to add transition probabilities to a genotype graph
    WeightedGenotypeGraphAllowingMultipleMutations
    Extension of WeightedGenotypeGraph that allows the reconstruction of genotype graphs with the acquisition of multiple mutation in a single transition when the are not better explanations.
    WeightedGenotypeGraphTest
